    <briefdescription>
<para><ref refid="class_hd_driver" kindref="compound">HdDriver</ref> represents a device object, commonly a render device, that is owned by the application and passed to <ref refid="class_hd_render_index" kindref="compound">HdRenderIndex</ref>. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>The RenderIndex passes it to the render delegate and rendering tasks. The application manages the lifetime (destruction) of <ref refid="class_hd_driver" kindref="compound">HdDriver</ref> and must ensure it remains valid while Hydra is running. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
